cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use ESI in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "ESI: Epistemic State Interface for Agent Memory"
abstract: >
  ESI is a drop-in standard that adds epistemic state (confidence, freshness)
  to any AI agent memory system. It addresses the core problem that agents
  forget information but do not know they forgot it — responding with equal
  confidence whether a memory is fresh or heavily degraded.
